title: Bug 7752: Export multiple files with the same file name under different directories to a zip file fails.
OB: When exporting multiple files with the same file name under different directories to a zip file, the export process fails.
EB: The zip file should successfully store files with the same name under different directories.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the software. 2. Navigate to the directories containing files with the same name. 3. Select the files and try to export them to a zip file.
